    "## Step 6: Implementing a Numeric Extraction Function\n",
    "\n",
    "A custom function is implemented to extract numeric values from text-based data fields.\n",
    "\n",
    "The function performs the following operations:\n",
    "\n",
    "1. Detects whether a value is stored as text\n",
    "2. Removes commas and formatting symbols\n",
    "3. Uses regular expressions to identify numeric patterns\n",
    "4. Converts the extracted value into a numerical data type\n",
    "\n",
    "This automated approach ensures consistent and scalable **data cleaning across multiple columns**."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 29,
   "id": "146cb363-ebe0-453f-b4a1-291c550f732e",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def extract_numeric(value):\n",
    "    if isinstance(value, str):\n",
    "\n",
    "        value = value.replace(\",\", \"\")\n",
    "        \n",
    "        # Extract numeric value... decimals or negative numbers\n",
    "        match = re.search(r'-?\\d+\\.?\\d*', value)\n",
    "        \n",
    "        if match:\n",
    "            return float(match.group())\n",
    "        else:\n",
    "            return np.nan\n",
    "    return value"
   ]
  },
